title: Bug 104630: Column icons don't show up in connecting derby database
OB: When expanding the Data Source in the Available Items sector, the table icons appear as expected. However, the column icons do not appear.
EB: In the Available Items sector, when expanding the Data Source by clicking the related icon, both table icons and column icons should be displayed.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Open the software application.
2. Navigate to the Available Items sector.
3. Locate the Data Source.
4. Click the related icon to expand the Data Source.
5. Confirm that the table icons and column icons do not appear.
